In this work we present Destiny a cognitive mobile guide for Olympics games in Brazil that identifies user characteristics to deliver content. It will help visitors, athletes, and athletes' parents to localize themselves and receive tailored historical, cultural and entertainment information at a particular point of interest (POI). The application will recommend places to go and show POI contents according to user context based on several attributes such as personality (closeness, curiosity, adventurous), nationality, favorite places already visited, trip length, price range and favorite sports